      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Private Law 4              : The law of wills and estates from a common law perspective. Topics considered include: intestate succession; interpretation of wills; testamentary autonomy and its limits; formal validity of wills; testamentary capacity and undue influence; revocation of wills; doctrine of lapse; survivorship; spousal protection and dependants' relief; capacity of beneficiaries.          </p>

