              <p>The following trans-systemic courses count for half their credit weight in each of the advanced common law and advanced civil law course lists above: </p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/cmpl-522" class="program-course-title">
              CMPL 522 Medical Liability (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
