                <h4> </h4>

    
              <p>Principles of Canadian Administrative Law </p>
<p>Requirement: Students must take at least one course (0-6 credits) from the following courses to meet this requirement:</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/bus1-432" class="program-course-title">
              BUS1 432 Bankruptcy and Insolvency (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-19292" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
